reviewText:
The material contained in this half hour video is outdated. It was published in 1981. It is not worth the cost of shipping. It does not deserve a one star rating.
If you buy, you will be wasting your money. It is a rip-off. In 1981 it would have been a rip-off.  I am surprised that Amazon would carry it. I am sorry I bought it; I would not even give it away.
